comment: No need for liposuction. You are already doing so well, and you are a great inspiration for many. I personally have been on a life style change since 2019. Lost 15 kilos from 95 kg with diet. And it was really really hard but watching your videos was always a good support to me. It always felt like I had a friend I could relate to. Since 2022 my weight didn't go down at all and I thought I would be overweight for the rest of my life. Again watching your videos have been such a great support and inspiration, since February 2023 I have finally lost another 15 kilos again. And for the first time in my life I have a normal weight and BMI. Like you said, it has to be a lifestyle rather than diet. We just have to keep fighting. I still have a long way to go and lose more weight but even losing 30 kgs feels like a big achievement. Thank you for always being a good friend and great support. Let's keep fighting together, but most importantly let's be happy and healthy while losing weight <3
